Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.19,0:00:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.76,0:00:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.23,0:00:22.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.77,0:00:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.88,0:00:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.09,0:00:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.89,0:00:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.17,0:01:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.61,0:01:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.92,0:01:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.62,0:01:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.24,0:01:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,离开地球的人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.38,0:01:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙殖民卫星的生活里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.28,0:01:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻找新的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.08,0:01:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，地球圈统一联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉正义及和平为名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以压倒性的军事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.29,0:01:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,压制着各个殖民卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.97,0:01:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作战名称[流星作战]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.40,0:01:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和联合反目的部份卫星居民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.11,0:01:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决定把伪装为流星的新武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送落地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，这次作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.13,0:02:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这情形怎样看\N你也比较像坏人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没受伤吧?小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三话\N[钢弹5机确认]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,处于被动了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.49,0:02:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的最终目的一日不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.16,0:02:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就只有这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果要先发制人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们会攻击地中海吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里是里欧的古老生产基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.60,0:02:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然联合也正在加强防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.27,0:02:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他们有点力有未逮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.34,0:02:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为艾亚利兹中队能胜任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.17,0:02:59.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.21,0:03:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于机动战士\N对战的能力相差太远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信不能和联合军合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.65,0:03:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.65,0:03:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的脸那样说着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.49,0:03:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消灭他们给我看，杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的最新机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坎沙也被击毁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.77,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,绝对不是很差的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.44,0:03:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遗憾\N那部受损的敌人新型机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.44,0:03:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的那么危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.41,0:03:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5名优秀部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.08,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,损失太大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉，今后我们怎办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.78,0:03:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,确认5机所在\N及调查他们的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.15,0:03:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的调查交给\N联合军的海军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.47,0:04:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它已经不在海底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们难以预测的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.17,0:04:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也可以说是胡乱行动的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.29,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呼吸数27
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.89,0:04:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脉搏57
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,体温34度c，正在上升
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.89,0:04:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.09,0:04:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以为刚才有变化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.16,0:04:29.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被捉住了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合的南面JAP地区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.42,0:04:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联合军第3医疗机关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.22,0:04:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,50楼特别治疗室吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莎莉少校，有联络进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们交给我们的那只光碟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太先进了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任何阅读方法也不接受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个男孩的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.44,0:05:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然连联合的电脑也不能分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.41,0:05:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.54,0:05:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他果然是叛乱份子的情报员吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.88,0:05:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还未肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,异常地锻炼过的肉体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.61,0:05:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,曾撞伤骨折的地方超过二百处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.68,0:05:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，外伤全是由枪伤造成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不可以说是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.39,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在普通家庭成长的少年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要使用药物吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用...成长时用药只会等于下毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.16,0:05:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.90,0:05:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,两部一模一样的马车弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你在黄色田野里弄饭盒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.64,0:05:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，我回来之后再帮你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，该去探一下病人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.22,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从敌人的路线分析来看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是先探知我们的动向\N然后才行动的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.46,0:06:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是在扬子江出现的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.09,0:06:07.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从这速度看来那不是飞行机种\N也就是说...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人真的造出那么多功能的机体吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.57,0:06:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在地中海的柯西嘉基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许能看到行动不明的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，也或许能当场击毁他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这部从扬子江来的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.61,0:06:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会出席柯西嘉基地的典礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他喜欢正面挑战联合的火力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我们看见的对手真可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.32,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样因达斯补给基地会被攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,祝他们好运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.16,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在只能那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太没有防备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.81,0:06:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么没有防备，我被看不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢绝探访!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.65,0:07:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的伤势那么严重吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把他带来这里的是你呢!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在这里等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是军队的莎莉少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个特别的男孩的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以告诉我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.03,0:07:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别的男孩?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.27,0:07:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就连你也要乖乖就范啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:52.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这种人能从我的嘴形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道我说什么吧!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是令人吃惊的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.11,0:08:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能脉搏和脑波不变就醒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.44,0:08:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很多事想问你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.48,0:08:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我来帮你离开这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是个非常有意思的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在粗野中，我感到高尚的一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得他和普通男孩无分别
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的名字是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.56,0:08:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫莉莉娜‧德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,德利安?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是那个\N德利安外务次官的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.27,0:08:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没教养的女儿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.67,0:08:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说了什么触怒你的话吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.24,0:08:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我能见他…希洛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛?他叫希洛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.25,0:08:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他是我非常要好的同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.39,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有变化吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，莎莉少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.13,0:08:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真过份!\N希洛为何会被绑住!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.33,0:08:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放了他!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.40,0:08:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他太强壮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们很怕他乱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.37,0:09:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以，我们不得已要把他绑起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能从他口中得到情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.77,0:09:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们至少能替他松绑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.24,0:09:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换言之他不是联合军的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.09,0:09:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不可以那么悠闲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.29,0:09:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点…拿消防器材...快!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!怎样解开它!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给我刀，我要从中切断
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.90,0:09:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你的手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.14,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很有决心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.44,0:09:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.11,0:09:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.20,0:10:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你做什么?\N快用降落伞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.31,0:10:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!你想死吗!?这家伙!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.58,0:10:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!想害我做恶梦啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从这里跳下去了吗!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!希洛!不可以死!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事到如今赶得及吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.11,0:10:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还活着!?难以置信!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得希望他不是敌人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.65,0:11:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…我究竟在做什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你想死的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但从那高度跌下来都不会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我劝你再想一个好一点的死法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.77,0:11:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会叫你相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.31,0:11:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但现在你什么也做不到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.62,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在公布军方发表的新闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日前因为原因不明的爆炸意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆战用机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.36,0:11:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,量产型里欧的生产大幅落后了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地中海的柯西嘉机动战士工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.40,0:11:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正全力赶工，应该能如期竣工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.10,0:11:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，为了查明原因及以防万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.10,0:11:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军队决定由SMS中队负责防卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.21,0:11:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该能见到杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我两小时内回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来我赶得及出席典礼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.60,0:12:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保拿巴司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出来这里始终太危险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.07,0:12:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!这是把我们的决心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉敌人及SMS的最好方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.81,0:12:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不须要SMS帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.08,0:12:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有这种藉口，他们才会来捣乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对地球圈统一联合军里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能够大幅扩张军备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特别机动战士部队[SMS]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.92,0:12:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不信任和反感的人为数也不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.39,0:12:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻的领导想建立新时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯.克修里那达上级特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是创立SMS的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.87,0:12:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他也是罗姆斐拉财团的干部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团是以重视传统的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奥索比亚贵族们为资金来源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他以那财力全力开发机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.55,0:13:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,SMS是个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.95,0:13:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只向联合提供机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还着手领导战争兵团的部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.06,0:13:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战场上的评价也很高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.06,0:13:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，在何时何地也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.66,0:13:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们拥有单独行动的特权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那格外引起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,久经战场的老兵们不满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.34,0:13:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是不容否定的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,误会战场是贵族娱乐的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.91,0:13:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们因为想杀戮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.08,0:13:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才资助军队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用倚靠他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.92,0:13:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有余地的行动\N也能避免无谓战火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.66,0:13:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要让血腥的SMS学习这兵法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，保拿巴司令\N即是不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:13:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然听闻他讨厌我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.64,0:14:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.47,0:14:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那样想我也没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.94,0:14:11.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,华卡特士，很久无见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉你看来也没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有我能出战的机体吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面，我有东西想给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好大啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是机动战士的原型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比里欧大一倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.67,0:14:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然古老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.07,0:14:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但看过杰克斯特尉\N的钢弹资料后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就想起这部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.71,0:14:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当时是试验品的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.88,0:14:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是柯西嘉出产的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.45,0:14:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.08,0:14:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是唯一一部机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.62,0:14:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拥有能和那资料匹敌的装甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不知道它是怎样制成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.46,0:14:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但要维持那强度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,体型就会太巨大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.26,0:15:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听闻现在机动战士的体型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是依照没那需要的标准制造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.43,0:15:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我记得这部机体叫[托尔吉斯]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把这机体完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.24,0:15:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能和钢弹对等决战了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你把它运离这工场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.64,0:15:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想死吗?华卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.88,0:15:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特尉你教我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.91,0:15:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[为将来的士兵而战]的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在支持着我的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.75,0:15:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，你比我更加勇敢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.76,0:15:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.06,0:15:31.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我依照你的教导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,经常当来袭的是最强的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.76,0:15:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,4部，有1部不会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.86,0:15:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只有这点情报\N对不起，华卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是少了1部我已很高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯特尉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.87,0:15:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请停止，保拿巴司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.57,0:15:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.28,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.85,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说敌人会来!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有笨蛋来挑战\N这么森严的防卫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.73,0:16:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.57,0:16:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次机会立即进行反击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全体跟我来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还只是看见1部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.71,0:16:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1部也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.60,0:16:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下降!急速下降!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷静点，敌人只有1部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,包围他把他消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.40,0:16:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷达完全无反应!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,监察摄影机…确认到了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.54,0:16:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倚靠机器才会变成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战术上，要打倒少数的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,断其退路，使用集中炮火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能比较肯定的取胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.29,0:17:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候，敌人司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.63,0:17:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,采取包围歼灭战\N的决定是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.04,0:17:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在掌握我的战斗力前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.04,0:17:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不应该采取行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么回事!竟然这么失败…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.38,0:17:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,协助司令后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.22,0:17:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里的人迎击敌人   知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们这班人!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.06,0:17:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们在那战斗力\N前也会被击毁吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.29,0:17:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,指示工场的资料组记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.39,0:17:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了将来的士兵!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.07,0:17:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接近战，只有那方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,准备完毕，随时可以出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.81,0:18:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保拿巴呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.35,0:18:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无线电联络说他没事
